[About 1/3 of the state's cases are in MSM, a clearly demonstrated high risk group, but the epidemiology of the other 2/3 of cases is not stated. It would be interesting to know if homeless individuals are a large part of the cohort as seems to be occurring in outbreaks of HAV in southern California and eastern Michigan. - Mod.LL

The state of Colorado can be located on the HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map at https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=5201341,903. Pueblo County can be seen on the map at http://geology.com/county-map/colorado-county-map.gif. - Sr.Tech.Ed.MJ]
